dc_description_s: This layer represents the outline for New Hampshire. New Hampshire; 1:250,000 statewide manuscript, obtained from NH Granit (NH state GIS program) in 1990. This layer was projected to the Massachusetts State Plane Mainland coordinate system, NAD83 datum, units meters, for use with all other MassGIS data. Please note that the layers vary in quality and are distributed for use only in regional mapping.
